WEBVTT

1
00:00:03.366 --> 00:00:05.600
Your Highness, you also bled earlier.

2
00:00:05.933 --> 00:00:07.666
Drink some warming medicine while it’s still hot.

3
00:00:22.300 --> 00:00:23.233
When you were young,

4
00:00:23.333 --> 00:00:25.366
I always had to prepare a lotus seed candy for you

5
00:00:25.733 --> 00:00:26.900
before you would take your medicine.

6
00:00:27.900 --> 00:00:28.833
Thank you.

7
00:00:34.900 --> 00:00:37.966
Li Gongguan, make sure to take good care of the Emperor with Dr. Hu.

8
00:00:37.966 --> 00:00:40.033
Lord Shen, come with me.

9
00:00:49.200 --> 00:00:51.466
Your Highness, where are you feeling unwell?

10
00:00:51.600 --> 00:00:53.600
Don’t worry, I’m fine.

11
00:00:53.600 --> 00:00:56.400
That’s good. What happened today?

12
00:00:56.400 --> 00:00:58.066
Why did the Emperor lose control suddenly?

13
00:00:58.666 --> 00:00:59.766
The Emperor, he—

14
00:01:01.200 --> 00:01:02.566
Your Majesty, I—

15
00:01:02.566 --> 00:01:04.666
have gathered all evidence regarding Prince Duan’s rebellion.

16
00:01:05.400 --> 00:01:06.600
Please review it, Your Majesty.

17
00:01:11.966 --> 00:01:13.900
This fool usually indulges in the changing of plants,

18
00:01:13.900 --> 00:01:14.800
accepting bribes and corruption.

19
00:01:14.933 --> 00:01:16.433
He enjoys playing with machinery.

20
00:01:16.600 --> 00:01:19.066
Without Prince Duan, I don’t know when it started,

21
00:01:19.333 --> 00:01:20.866
but in the court, he caused chaos,

22
00:01:21.100 --> 00:01:22.866
betraying loyal officials and harming the people.

23
00:01:22.933 --> 00:01:25.300
He even contacted enemy states.

24
00:01:25.466 --> 00:01:26.966
What a bold move.
